title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 1 2022

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3:

DeSantis slaps down media on Nazi ridiculousness. Poll: Dems, Biden down big in Florida. Is Tom Brady the G.O.A.T. of American team sports? Clay gives a proclamation. Buck joshingly asked: "I'm seeing this today about Tom Brady, and there was this big countdown to whether he's retired or not. Wasn't he already retired?" Bad takes from when the Pats drafted Brady. CNN's media know-it-all Brian Stelter on Rogan. Who do you trust more: CNN or Joe Rogan? C&B PSA: Freeing America, One Mask at a Time. Georgetown protesters demand ouster of professor, crying rooms.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
